@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_bwytum(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((0.03 + (v0 + 0.38 * v2 + 0.73)) - wp.sin(0.67))
    v2 = wp.abs((wp.sin(v1 + 0.36) / wp.cos(v1 + 0.50)))
    v0 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
